sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant NextJS as Next.js Router
    participant Factory as SafeApi Factory
    participant Logic as Business Logic
    participant ErrorHandler as Error Handler

    Client->>NextJS: POST /api/resource
    activate NextJS

    NextJS->>Factory: Invoke Handler
    activate Factory

    Note over Factory: 1. Request Parsing

    alt Malformed JSON
        Factory-->>Client: 400 Bad Request
    else Valid JSON

        Note over Factory: 2. Zod Validation

        alt Invalid Schema
            Factory-->>Client: 400 Bad Request
        else Valid Schema

            Factory->>Logic: Run Handler({ body }, context)
            activate Logic

            alt Execution Succeeded
                Logic-->>Factory: Return Data Object
                Factory-->>Client: 200 OK (JSON)
            else Execution Failed
                Factory->>ErrorHandler: handleApiError(error)
                activate ErrorHandler
                Note right of ErrorHandler: Normalize -> Log
                ErrorHandler-->>Factory: Return NextResponse
                deactivate ErrorHandler

                Factory-->>Client: 4xx / 5xx JSON Response
            end
        end
    end

    deactivate Factory
    deactivate NextJS
